---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="404 · 找不到這條浪 — 衝浪研究室"
      description="這個位置沒有 spot。回到 8 期主題索引看看。">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .nf-page {
        max-width: 880px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 28px 100px;
        font-family: var(--serif);
      }
      .nf-strip {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 10px 0;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 10.5px;
        letter-spacing: .14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
        margin-bottom: 36px;
      }
      .nf-strip .err { color: var(--vermillion); font-weight: 700; }
      .nf-num {
        font-family: var(--display);
        font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 240px);
        line-height: .85;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -.02em;
        color: var(--vermillion);
      }
      .nf-num .small {
        display: block;
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: .12em;
        letter-spacing: .25em;
        color: var(--ink);
        margin-top: 14px;
      }
      .nf-body {
        margin: 28px 0 36px;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--ink);
        max-width: 56ch;
      }
      .nf-body .ch { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 22px; }
      .nf-body .en { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12.5px; letter-spacing: .08em; opacity: .8; }
      .nf-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        padding-top: 28px;
        border-top: 3px double var(--ink);
      }
      .nf-actions a {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 11.5px;
        letter-spacing: .12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 10px 16px 8px;
        border: 1.6px solid var(--ink);
        color: var(--ink);
        background: var(--paper);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: transform .12s;
      }
      .nf-actions a:hover {
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
        transform: translate(-2px,-2px);
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--vermillion);
      }
      .nf-actions a.primary {
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
      }
      .nf-actions a.primary:hover {
        background: var(--vermillion);
        color: var(--paper);
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
      }
      .nf-issues {
        margin-top: 48px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
        gap: 0;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      }
      .nf-issues a {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: 14px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
        color: var(--ink);
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .nf-issues a:hover { background: var(--paper-deep); }
      .nf-issues a .no {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 10px;
        letter-spacing: .12em;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <main class="nf-page">
    <div class="nf-strip">
      <div><span class="err">● ERROR 404</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; PAGE NOT FOUND</div>
      <div>衝浪研究室 · THE SURF STUDY</div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="nf-num">404<span class="small">這條浪沒撿到</span></h1>

    <div class="nf-body">
      <span class="ch">你找的這個位置 outside 太遠了。</span>
      <span class="en">The break you're paddling for isn't here. The URL may be mistyped, the page may have been renumbered, or this issue isn't published yet.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="nf-actions">
      <a href="/" class="primary">← 回到 NO. 008 封面</a>
      <a href="/bali">NO. 001 / Bali</a>
      <a href="/boards">NO. 007 / Boards</a>
      <a href="/bigwave">NO. 008 / Big Wave</a>
    </div>

    <nav class="nf-issues" aria-label="所有期數">
      <a href="/bali"><span>峇里島 Bali</span><span class="no">001</span></a>
      <a href="/hainan"><span>海南 Hainan</span><span class="no">002</span></a>
      <a href="/australia"><span>澳洲 Australia</span><span class="no">003</span></a>
      <a href="/taiwan"><span>台灣 Taiwan</span><span class="no">004</span></a>
      <a href="/japan"><span>日本 Japan</span><span class="no">005</span></a>
      <a href="/korea"><span>韓國 Korea</span><span class="no">006</span></a>
      <a href="/boards"><span>Board Lab</span><span class="no">007</span></a>
      <a href="/bigwave"><span>Big Wave</span><span class="no">008</span></a>
    </nav>
  </main>
</Base>
